<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.968.54228.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Prathapanius fortis sp. nov. A Holotype, arrow pointing to spine on front trochanter B paratype, arrow pointing to spine on front trochanter C paratype, arrow pointing to protibial ridges." ;
