<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.968.54228.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Prathapanius fortis sp. nov., paratypes. A Bifid claws B male, prothoracic leg and maxillary palpi C female, dorsal aspect D female, ventral aspect." ;
