    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.968.54228.figure5>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Prathapanius fortis sp. nov., paratype. A Median lobe of aedeagus, lateral aspect B median lobe of aedeagus, dorsal aspect C median lobe of aedeagus, ventral aspect D tegmen, dorsal aspect E tegmen, lateral aspect, x = ventral carina on either side of depression, y = fin-like structure." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/453187" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

